rows.label: tev011201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the recently discovered survivors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Corwin if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the duties of a Pathfinder.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the duties of a Pathfinder.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0001
rows.name:
You mean the lone survivor found in Starfall Basin?
Pretty crazy, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0003
rows.name:
My team has found plenty of Lifepods that were
jettisoned from the White Whale as it crashed, but they
were all in terrible shape and... Well, no survivors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0004
rows.name: So it seems this new survivor got incredibly lucky.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0005
rows.name:
And if my experience has taught me anything,
I'd expect him or her to live a long life and
accomplish many great things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0006
rows.name:
As someone who fell from the peak of Mt. Everest
and actually lived to tell about it, take it from me.
I know what I'm talking about.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0009
rows.name:
Well, Team Corwin specializes in exploring the most
dangerous parts of Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0010
rows.name:
As you'd imagine, we suffer a lot of casualties doing it.
All but the bravest of Pathfinders quickly transfer to
other teams.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0011
rows.name:
As a result, we're undermanned. We're always trying to
recruit new members, but there aren't many BLADEs
with the guts to join us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0012
rows.name:
At the moment, all that's left is myself, Raleigh, Peter,
the new guy, Bates, and my old friends from way back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0013
rows.name: That's all. It's a pretty sad state of affairs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0014
rows.name:
It's breaking my heart. What happened to all the
eager new recruits brimming with frontier spirit?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0022
rows.name:
It ain't easy to accomplish much on this planet without
reliable information.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0023
rows.name:
That's why we enter unexplored areas ahead of the
other divisions and plant data probes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0024
rows.name:
Once installed, a data probe will send back tons of
useful information over FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0025
rows.name:
Sure, the job's dangerous, but getting to see a new
place before anyone else? Ain't no mission more
exciting than that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0026
rows.name:
For a longtime adventurer like me, it's pretty much the
gig of my dreams.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0042
rows.name:
I did a lot of successful expeditions before I ever
boarded the White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0043
rows.name:
The toughest of them all was the many years I spent
surveying the surface of the Moon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0044
rows.name:
But that job didn't hold a candle to how hard it is
reaching these damned FrontierNav probe placement
sites.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0045
rows.name:
At least this planet has oxygen—but that's hardly worth
facing all the nasty indigens![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0046
rows.name:
Our mission is all about slipping past the beasties to
reach FrontierNav probe sites that are invariably at the
least-accessible points on the entire planet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0047
rows.name:
We put our lives on the line every day, but that just
makes the triumph all the sweeter when we do reach
our target.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Corwin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0048
rows.name: Well, I just saved Bates's sorry ass, for one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0049
rows.name:
But during that mission, a gal named Tempera showed
up in this weird black Skell.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0050
rows.name:
It was closing in on me and Raleigh, so we really had
to haul ass outta there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0051
rows.name:
That crazy gal was carrying on about her mom or her
big sister or...something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0052
rows.name:
Anyway, you better watch out—we still got a whole
lot of enemies out there. This planet ain't ours yet.
Not by a long shot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL2011
rows.name: Ask Corwin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0053
rows.name:
Hey, how's it going, [ST:playername ]!
Thanks for your help with that whole Bates thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0054
rows.name:
I've been trying to track down the black Skell that
attacked you and Bates.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0055
rows.name:
If you find out anything about it, could you give me
a heads-up?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0056
rows.name:
Someone needs to be taught a lesson about picking
fights with Team Corwin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL3011
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the duties of a Pathfinder.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask Corwin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL3031
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the Lifehold.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0057
rows.name:
I did a lot of successful expeditions before I ever
boarded the White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0058
rows.name:
The toughest of them all was the many years I spent
surveying the surface of the Moon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0059
rows.name:
But that job didn't hold a candle to how hard it is
reaching these damned FrontierNav probe placement
sites.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0060
rows.name:
At least this planet has oxygen—but that's hardly worth
facing all the nasty indigens![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0063
rows.name:
And on top of that, now we got all these weird xenos
gunning for us. We haven't had a single expedition
ever go smoothly. Not a single one![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0064
rows.name:
But that just makes the triumph all the sweeter when
we do reach our target, right? I'm sure you know
what I'm talking about.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0067
rows.name:
Well, I've had a pretty rough time of it,
but it ain't dampened my frontier spirit any.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0068
rows.name:
Actually, my spirit is burning hotter than ever,
despite the fact I just lost a friend from way back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0069
rows.name:
Bates is actually starting to earn his keep, and Peter?
Man, that guy's got the boundless curiosity of a true
adventurer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0070
rows.name:
And we've still got Raleigh loving us all to pieces,
so I'm confident Team Corwin's gonna dust itself off
and reclaim its past glory.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0071
rows.name:
Honestly, I'd ask 'em to transfer you onto my team,
but I know there's no way Elma would give you up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0072
rows.name:
No matter. Let's both just keep on chasing those
sweet Miran dreams.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0078
rows.name:
So is it true? You got back the comm device with the
coordinates of the Lifehold Core?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0079
rows.name:
To be honest, I was hoping it'd be Team Corwin
bringing back that glory, but a win's a win.
Well done, my friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0080
rows.name:
Team Corwin's not exactly in the best of shape after all
that trouble we had earlier, but you better believe we'll
fight to the last man in the final battle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0081
rows.name:
Our real bodies? Humanity's future?
I'm gonna take it back with my own two hands![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_SEL3041
rows.name: Ask Corwin about the Lifehold Core.

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0082
rows.name:
I wanna stand barefoot on the surface of Mira and feel
the true frontier spirit course through my veins.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0083
rows.name:
I wonder how long it's gonna take before the
Lifehold is up and running again?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0084
rows.name:
I know a research party went into the Lifehold Core,
but I haven't heard a word about what they've been
doing there. Hope that's not a bad sign.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev011201_MSG0085
rows.name:
Ah, I gotta stop thinking like that.
It ain't like me to worry.[ST:wait ]
